.SH NAME
lat_sig \- select benchmark
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lat_ctx 
[
.I "-P <parallelism>"
]
[
.I "-W <warmups>"
]
[
.I "-N <repetitions>"
]
.I "install|catch|prot"
[
.I "file"
]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B lat_sig
measures the time to install and catch signals.  It can also measure
the time to catch a protection fault.
